so I ran. That's all.

507
00:22:02,125 --> 00:22:03,875
We need more details.

508
00:22:03,958 --> 00:22:05,958
Wasn't just the barghest
that attacked you.

509
00:22:06,041 --> 00:22:10,458
Uh! The Giant of the
East sent his minions.

510
00:22:10,541 --> 00:22:12,333
The Giant of the East?

511
00:22:12,416 --> 00:22:14,125
And the Demon Snake of the West.

512
00:22:14,208 --> 00:22:17,416
He joined up with him.
War is coming.

